OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has called for Kemi
OL,8,FBadenoch to sack shadow justice
OL,9,Fsecretary Nick Timothy after he said
OL,10,Fmass Muslim public prayer was an "act
OL,11,Fof domination and division".
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister said during Prime
OL,14,FMinister's Questions that Mrs Badenoch
OL,15,Fshould "denounce" Mr Timothy's
OL,16,Fcomments and dismiss him. He had
OL,17,Fpreviously been a senior adviser to
OL,18,FBaroness Theresa May when she was
OL,19,Fprime minister.
OL,26,@rD@bOUsD@[O]wD@HOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FAfter an event at Trafalgar Square at
OL,8,Fthe weekend, which was attended by
OL,9,FLondon Mayor Sir Sadiq Khan, Mr
OL,10,FTimothy posted on X on Tuesday: "Mass
OL,11,Fritual prayer in public places is an
OL,12,Fact of domination."
OL,14,FHe continued: "Perform these rituals
OL,15,Fin mosques if you wish. But they are
OL,16,Fnot welcome in our public places and
OL,17,Fshared institutions."
OL,26,@rD@aOUtD@SO]vD@OOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FSimilar religious gatherings have long
OL,8,Ftaken place in the capital city, such
OL,9,Fas the Jewish celebration of Chanukah
OL,10,Fand Easter Sunday processions.
OL,12,FSir Keir said the comments meant the
OL,13,FConservative Party had become aligned
OL,14,Fwith Tommy Robinson, after Mr
OL,15,FRobinson, whose real name is Stephen
OL,16,FYaxley-Lennon, had posted supportively
OL,17,Fof Mr Timothy's comments.
OL,19,FThe Prime Minister said it showed the
OL,20,FTories had a "problem with Muslims".
OL,26,@|D@NOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FResponding to a question from Mrs
OL,8,FBadenoch, Sir Keir said: "She
OL,9,Fappointed the shadow justice
OL,10,Fsecretary. He said last night that
OL,11,FMuslims praying in public, including
OL,12,Fthe mayor of London, practising his
OL,13,Ffaith, are not welcome.
OL,15,F"He described it as an act of
OL,16,Fdomination. Straight from the Islamist
OL,17,Fplaybook. If he was in my team, he'd
OL,18,Fbe gone. It's utterly appalling. She
OL,19,Fshould denounce his comments and she
OL,20,Fshould sack him."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUwD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FMrs Badenoch said Mr Timothy was
OL,8,F"defending British values" rather than
OL,9,F"abolishing jury trials", drawing
OL,10,Fcomparisons with Justice Secretary
OL,11,FDavid Lammy.
OL,13,F"I know who I would rather have
OL,14,Fsitting on the front bench next to me,
OL,15,Fand it's not him," Mrs Badenoch said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@ZO]qD@AOUqD@XO]uD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FSir Keir came back at Mrs Badenoch and
OL,8,Fsaid: "Her position is that the shadow
OL,9,Fjustice secretary is defending British
OL,10,Fvalues when he says Muslims praying
OL,11,Ftogether in Trafalgar Square are not
OL,12,Fwelcome.
OL,14,F"Even Tommy Robinson, I can hardly
OL,15,Fbelieve I'm saying this, has said
OL,16,Ftoday that if the shadow justice
OL,17,Fsecretary had made these hateful
OL,18,Fcomments two years ago the
OL,19,FConservative Party would have kicked
OL,20,Fhim out.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"Tommy Robinson isn't some sort of
OL,8,Fmoral signpost, he was pointing out
OL,9,Fhow much their party has changed.
OL,10,FThey're more inclined to his views,
OL,11,Fand he's right about that. The fact
OL,12,Fhe's sitting on her front bench shows
OL,13,Fshe's too weak and has got absolutely
OL,14,Fno judgment."
OL,16,FMr Timothy's full post on X had read:
OL,17,F"Too many are too polite to say this.
OL,18,FBut mass ritual prayer in public
OL,19,Fplaces is an act of domination.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@MO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"The Adhan ` which declares there is
OL,8,Fno god but Allah and Muhammad is his
OL,9,Fmessenger ` is, when called in a
OL,10,Fpublic place, a declaration of
OL,11,Fdomination.
OL,13,F"Perform these rituals in mosques if
OL,14,Fyou wish. But they are not welcome in
OL,15,Four public places and shared
OL,16,Finstitutions.
OL,18,F"And given their explicit repudiation
OL,19,Fof Christianity they certainly do not
OL,20,Fbelong in our churches and cathedrals.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"I am not suggesting everybody at
OL,8,FTrafalgar Square last night is an
OL,9,FIslamist. But the domination of public
OL,10,Fplaces is straight from the Islamist
OL,11,Fplaybook.
OL,13,F"Trafalgar Square belongs to all of
OL,14,Fus. It is a national memorial to our
OL,15,Findependence and our salvation.
OL,17,F"Last night was not like a televised
OL,18,Ffootball match or a St Patrick's Day
OL,19,Fcelebration. It was an act of
OL,20,Fdomination and therefore division.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"It shouldn't happen again."
OL,9,FAs Mrs Badenoch continued to ask Sir
OL,10,FKeir about whether he had properly
OL,11,Fvetted Lord Peter Mandelson when he
OL,12,Fwas appointed UK ambassador to the US,
OL,13,Fthe Prime Minister replied by drawing
OL,14,Fattention to Mr Timothy's post.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FHe said: "When I see religious events
OL,8,Fin Trafalgar Square, when I see Hindus
OL,9,Fcelebrating Diwali, when I see Jews
OL,10,Fcelebrating Chanukah live, when I see
OL,11,FChristians performing the Passion of
OL,12,Fthe Christ, or Muslims praying, that
OL,13,Fshows the great strength of our
OL,14,Fdiverse city and country.
OL,16,F"I've never heard her party call out
OL,17,Fanything other than the Muslim events.
OL,18,FIt's only when Muslims are praying.
OL,19,FThe only conclusion is the Tory Party
OL,20,Fhas got a problem with Muslims."
OL,26,@oD@JOUxD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FHe added: "She's utterly irrelevant
OL,8,Fand she's got no judgment."
OL,10,FHe continued: "The failure to condemn
OL,11,Fand sack the shadow justice secretary
OL,12,Ffor the poison and division that he
OL,13,Fspreads, it's turning out to be quite
OL,14,Fa month for the leader of the
OL,15,Fopposition who claims she never makes
OL,16,Fany mistakes."
OL,18,FA spokesman for Mrs Badenoch said Mr
OL,19,FTimothy's comments were based on
OL,20,Ffootage showing segregated males
OL,21,Fpraying at the event.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@[O]rD@OOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FHe said: "The Conservative Party
OL,8,Fbelieves in British values and those
OL,9,FBritish values mean we are an open and
OL,10,Fopen and tolerant society, but with
OL,11,Fboundaries.
OL,13,F"And freedom of religion does not mean
OL,14,Fthe freedom to do anything. It comes
OL,15,Fwith responsibilities.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1773940276
OL,3,CStarmer says Badenoch should sack
OL,4,Cshadow justice secretary over Muslim
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"People are free to practice their
OL,8,Ffaith, but that practice does not
OL,9,Frequire exclusionary use of our shared
OL,10,Fcivic spaces. That is not about
OL,11,Fworship. It becomes something else
OL,12,Fwhich undermines social cohesion. So
OL,13,Fthat is where we draw the line. And
OL,14,Fthat is what Nick Timothy was talking
OL,15,Fabout."
OL,17,FAsked about other pictures showing
OL,18,Fwomen at the event, the spokesman said
OL,19,Fthey were "outside the barriers".
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@GO]{D@KOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
